---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Users & Groups - Drizby"
  description="Unlimited users with no per-seat pricing. Role-based access control, group-based visibility, and team management built in."
  ogImage="https://www.drizby.com/images/drizby_groups.png"
  canonicalPath="/features/users-and-groups"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://www.drizby.com" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Features", "item": "https://www.drizby.com/#features" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Users & Groups", "item": "https://www.drizby.com/features/users-and-groups" }
    ]
  })} />
  <main class="feature-page">
    <a href="/" class="breadcrumb">&larr; Back to Home</a>

    <section class="hero">
      <h1>Users & Groups</h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">Built for an agentic world &mdash; no per-seat pricing.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Authentication</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Multiple sign-in methods out of the box. Enable one or combine them to suit your team.</p>
      <div class="auth-providers">
        <div class="auth-provider">
          <img class="auth-logo" src="/images/auth-logos/password.svg" alt="Password" />
          <h3>Password</h3>
          <p>Email &amp; password with admin approval for new registrations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="auth-provider">
          <img class="auth-logo" src="/images/auth-logos/magic-link.svg" alt="Magic Link" />
          <h3>Magic Link</h3>
          <p>Passwordless sign-in via one-time email link.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="auth-provider">
          <img class="auth-logo" src="/images/auth-logos/google.svg" alt="Google" />
          <h3>Google</h3>
          <p>Google Workspace and personal accounts via OAuth.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="auth-provider">
          <img class="auth-logo" src="/images/auth-logos/github.svg" alt="GitHub" />
          <h3>GitHub</h3>
          <p>Sign in with GitHub accounts. Great for developer teams.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="auth-provider">
          <img class="auth-logo" src="/images/auth-logos/gitlab.svg" alt="GitLab" />
          <h3>GitLab</h3>
          <p>GitLab OAuth with PKCE for self-managed and SaaS instances.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="auth-provider">
          <img class="auth-logo" src="/images/auth-logos/microsoft.svg" alt="Microsoft" />
          <h3>Microsoft</h3>
          <p>Azure AD / Entra ID with PKCE. Supports single and multi-tenant.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="auth-provider">
          <img class="auth-logo" src="/images/auth-logos/slack.svg" alt="Slack" />
          <h3>Slack</h3>
          <p>Slack OpenID Connect for teams already on Slack.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="card card-highlight">
        <h2>No Per-User Limits</h2>
        <p>In a world where AI agents query data alongside humans, per-seat pricing doesn't make sense. Drizby treats every user the same &mdash; whether they're a person on your team or an AI assistant connecting via MCP. Self-hosted instances have zero user limits by design. Drizby Cloud charges based on running instance minutes, not the number of users or connected agents.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="screenshot-container">
        <figure>
          <img src="/images/drizby_groups.png" alt="Drizby users and groups management" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption>Team management with users, roles, and group-based visibility</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Role-Based Access Control</h2>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Admin Role</h3>
          <p>Full access to all settings, connections, users, and content. Manage database connections, configure AI providers, and control the MCP server.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Member Role</h3>
          <p>Access dashboards, notebooks, and the analysis builder. Create and share content with the team. No access to system settings or connections.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Group-Based Visibility</h2>
      <div class="card">
        <p>Organise users into groups and control who sees what. Dashboards and notebooks can be scoped to specific groups, so teams only see the content that's relevant to them. No complex permission matrices &mdash; just simple, intuitive group assignments.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Built for Teams</h2>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Admin Approval</h3>
          <p>New user registrations require admin approval, so you control who joins your instance. Pending users can't access any data until approved.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Auto-Accept Domains</h3>
          <p>Configure trusted email domains so users from your organisation are automatically approved as members when they sign in via OAuth or magic link.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Tenant Isolation</h3>
          <p>Each Drizby Cloud instance is fully isolated per tenant. For multi-tenant analytics within an instance, you can model organisation scoping directly into your cubes using the semantic layer's security context.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Session Security</h3>
          <p>Secure session-based authentication with HTTP-only cookies. Sessions auto-expire to limit exposure. Optional encryption at rest for stored secrets.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h2>Simple Pricing</h2>
        <div class="pricing-grid">
          <div class="pricing-option">
            <h3>Self-Hosted</h3>
            <p class="pricing-price">Free</p>
            <p>MIT licensed, unlimited users, unlimited dashboards, unlimited notebooks. Run it on your own infrastructure with Docker.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pricing-option">
            <h3>Drizby Cloud</h3>
            <p class="pricing-price">Instance minutes</p>
            <p>Pay for running time, not users. Your whole team gets access &mdash; no per-seat fees, no user tiers, no surprises.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section cta-section">
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://github.com/cliftonc/drizby" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <svg class="gh-icon" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 0C3.58 0 0 3.58 0 8c0 3.54 2.29 6.53 5.47 7.59.4.07.55-.17.55-.38 0-.19-.01-.82-.01-1.49-2.01.37-2.53-.49-2.69-.94-.09-.23-.48-.94-.82-1.13-.28-.15-.68-.52-.01-.53.63-.01 1.08.58 1.23.82.72 1.21 1.87.87 2.33.66.07-.52.28-.87.51-1.07-1.78-.2-3.64-.89-3.64-3.95 0-.87.31-1.59.82-2.15-.08-.2-.36-1.02.08-2.12 0 0 .67-.21 2.2.82.64-.18 1.32-.27 2-.27.68 0 1.36.09 2 .27 1.53-1.04 2.2-.82 2.2-.82.44 1.1.16 1.92.08 2.12.51.56.82 1.27.82 2.15 0 3.07-1.87 3.75-3.65 3.95.29.25.54.73.54 1.48 0 1.07-.01 1.93-.01 2.2 0 .21.15.46.55.38A8.013 8.013 0 0016 8c0-4.42-3.58-8-8-8z"/></svg>
          Self-Host Free
        </a>
        <a class="btn" href="https://cloud.drizby.com/register" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Try Drizby Cloud</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .feature-page {
    max-width: 1150px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }
  .breadcrumb:hover { color: var(--accent-hover); }

  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--text) 0%, var(--accent-hover) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  .hero-desc {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .content-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--text) 0%, var(--accent-hover) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .card h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .card p { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; font-size: 0.95rem; }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    background: #0891b2;
    color: #fff;
    vertical-align: middle;
    margin-left: 0.4rem;
  }

  .card-highlight {
    border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--surface) 0%, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.05) 100%);
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .screenshot-container figure {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .screenshot-container figure:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
  }
  .screenshot-container img { width: 100%; display: block; }
  .screenshot-container figcaption {
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pricing-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  .pricing-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .pricing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  .pricing-option {
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .pricing-option:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .pricing-option h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .pricing-price {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .pricing-option p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.5; }

  .cta-section { text-align: center; }
  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.65rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
  }
  .btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--text); }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--accent-hover);
    border-color: var(--accent-hover);
    color: #fff;
  }
  .gh-icon { width: 1em; height: 1em; }

  .section-desc {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .auth-providers {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(140px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .auth-provider {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .auth-provider:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .auth-provider h3 {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }
  .auth-provider p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .auth-logo {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
    .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .pricing-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .auth-providers { grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(120px, 1fr)); }
  }
</style>
